19 BE IT ENACTED BY THE GENERAL ASSEMBLY OF THE STATE OF ARKANSAS:
20
21 SECTION 1. Arkansas Code Title 23, Chapter 79, is amended to add an
22 additional subchapter to read as follows:
23
24 Subchapter 29 — Coverage for Noninvasive Ventilators
25
26 23-79-2901. Definitions.
27 As used in this subchapter:
28 (1) "Enrollee" means an individual entitled to coverage of
29 healthcare services from a healthcare insurer;
30 (2)(A) "Health benefit plan" means:
31 (i) An individual, blanket, or group plan, policy,
32 or contract for healthcare services issued, renewed, or extended in this
33 state by a healthcare insurer, health maintenance organization, hospital
34 medical service corporation, or self-insured governmental or church plan in
35 this state; and
36 (ii) Any health benefit program receiving state or
